      "content": "Okay, I see. But to be blunt, if I tell the Board there's an \"unidentified pathway interaction\" causing drop-offs, they're going to freeze the funding immediately for a full audit. They need certainty. If we look at the predictive modeling strictly on the successful responders, can you provide a high-confidence projection that we can use to justify the next round of investment despite this noise?",
